<h2>Lump or bulge, Sore tongue, Swollen tongue and White patches on tongue</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms lump or bulge, sore tongue, swollen tongue and white patches on tongue including Thermal burn of mouth or tongue, Drug allergy, and Thrush (infants and children).</p>
<p>There  are 12 conditions  associated with lump or bulge, sore tongue, swollen tongue and white patches on tongue. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
